<db:para>This is a variety of examples that cover the entire range of the the Qt Bluetooth API. You will find them in their own documentation but they are also accessible from here.</db:para>
<db:section xml:id="c-tutorial">
<db:title>C++ Tutorial</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qtbluetooth-btchat-example.xml">Bluetooth Chat</db:link> example contains a tutorial on how to use the C++ API to create a RFCOMM server and client, and exchange data between them.</db:para>
</db:section>
